"{\"uid\": \"myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com-news-michael-phelps-closes-olympics-with-23rd-gold-medal-in-relay\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe Now  RIO DE JANEIRO, Aug 14:\\u00a0\\u00a0Michael\\u00a0Phelps\\u00a0closed out the Rio Olympics in the only way imaginable.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 48, \"end\": 54, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999998153726, \"rank\": 1.8474670465707606e-10, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}, {\"begin\": 70, \"end\": 82, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9140075097942994e-17, \"text\": \"Rio Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gold.\", \"from\": 112, \"to\": 117, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Phelps\\u00a0put the United States ahead to stay on the butterfly leg and Nathan Adrian finished it off, giving the most decorated athlete in Olympic history his 23rd career gold medal.\", \"from\": 119, \"to\": 298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 134, \"end\": 147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7240006944950054, \"rank\": 0.3812087914881227, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 187, \"end\": 200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nathan_Adrian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nathan Adrian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nathan_Adrian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nathan_Adrian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If that was the end, and\\u00a0Phelps\\u00a0insists it is, what a way to go.\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 364, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 325, \"end\": 331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999998153726, \"rank\": 1.8474670465707606e-10, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Phelps\\u00a0said that Saturday was how he wanted to finish his career.\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 431, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is how I wanted to finish my career,\\\"\\u00a0Phelps\\u00a0said.\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 489, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 477, \"end\": 483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999998153726, \"rank\": 1.8474670465707606e-10, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Getting off the bus walking into the pool tonight, I pretty much felt myself starting to cry.\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Last time putting on a suit.\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 613, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Last time walking out in front of thousands of people representing my country.\\\"\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As Adrian touched the wall to finish off the victory,\\u00a0Phelps\\u00a0gathered the other relay swimmers, Ryan Murphy and Cody Miller, in his arms.\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 832, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 749, \"end\": 755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999998153726, \"rank\": 1.8474670465707606e-10, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}, {\"begin\": 791, \"end\": 802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Francisco_Giants_minor_league_players\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3526676755926215e-15, \"text\": \"Ryan Murphy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Francisco_Giants_minor_league_players\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Francisco_Giants_minor_league_players\"}, {\"begin\": 807, \"end\": 818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Miller\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cody Miller\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Miller\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Miller\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One night after his only setback in Rio, an upset loss to Joseph Schooling in the 100 fly,\\u00a0Phelps\\u00a0was back on top.\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 869, \"end\": 872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999802448638124, \"rank\": 1.975552656602611e-05, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 891, \"end\": 907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joseph_Schooling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Joseph Schooling\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joseph_Schooling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joseph_Schooling\"}, {\"begin\": 924, \"end\": 930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999998153726, \"rank\": 1.8474670465707606e-10, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the stands, his fiancee, Nicole Johnson, bounced along to the music with their son, 3-month-old Boomer, cradled in her arms.\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 977, \"end\": 991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Johnson_(Miss_America)\", \"score\": 0.6172101084678671, \"rank\": 0.5769230769232526, \"text\": \"Nicole Johnson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Johnson_(Miss_America)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Johnson_(Miss_America)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Phelps\\u00a0is eager to spend a lot more time with them.\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1078, \"end\": 1084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999998153726, \"rank\": 1.8474670465707606e-10, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He plans to marry Johnson after the Olympics and said he wants to watch his son grow, maybe even dole out a swimming lesson or two.\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1261, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1148, \"end\": 1155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"score\": 0.9039146160296924, \"rank\": 0.1007043158981421, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of the U.S. swim team was in the stands to watch\\u00a0Phelps' finale, 